#

Hearty Minestrone Soup

45 min
$15
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Gluten (if using regular pasta)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh FiberLow Fat

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A nourishing and vibrant soup loaded with seasonal vegetables, beans, and pasta, perfect for a wholesome meal.

Ingredients

  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • onion: 1, diced
  • carrots: 2, chopped
  • celery: 2 stalks, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • zucchini: 1, diced
  • green beans: 1 cup, chopped
  • diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • canned kidney beans: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • pasta (small shape): 1 cup
  • spinach or kale: 2 cups, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
  • parmesan cheese (optional): for serving
